security_common_cookie


cookie检查


denylist
array[string]
黑名单列表，匹配cookie中的关键字，命中后拦截用户请求。

status
integer，默认值，403
拦截后，响应的状态码

message
string，
拦截后，响应的信息

bypass_missing
boolean，默认值，true
当设置为 true 时，如果cookie请求头不存在或格式有误时，将绕过检查。

说明：





事例：

添加插件
curl -L -X PUT 'http://127.0.0.1:9990/edge/admin/global_rules/6001' -H 'X-API-KEY: f9357106bff442f89d4de7169c37c61e' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' --data-raw '{
    "desc": "security_common",
    "plugins": {
        "security_common_cookie": {
            "bypass_missing": true,
            "denylist": [
                "jndi\\:(?:ldap|rmi|iiop|iiopname|corbaname|dns|nis)",
                "\\.\\./",
                "\\:\\$",
                "\\$\\{",
                "(?:^|\\W)select\\W.+\\W(?:from|limit)\\W",
                "(?:(union(.*?)select))",
                "sleep\\((\\s*)(\\d*)(\\s*)\\)",
                "benchmark\\((.*)\\,(.*)\\)",
                "base64_decode\\(",
                "(?:from\\W+information_schema\\W)",
                "(?:(?:current_)user|database|schema|connection_id)\\s*\\(",
                "(?:etc/\\W*passwd)",
                "into(\\s+)+(?:dump|out)file\\s*",
                "group\\s+by.+\\(",
                "xwork.MethodAccessor",
                "(?:define|eval|file_get_contents|include|require|require_once|shell_exec|phpinfo|system|passthru|preg_\\w+|execute|echo|print|print_r|var_dump|(fp)open|alert|showmodaldialog)\\(",
                "xwork\\.MethodAccessor",
                "(?:gopher|doc|php|glob|file|phar|zlib|ftp|ldap|dict|ogg|data)\\:\\/",
                "java\\.lang",
                "\\$_(?:GET|post|cookie|files|session|env|phplib|GLOBALS|SERVER)\\["
            ]
        }
    }
}'

测试
curl -L -X GET 'http://127.0.0.1:9980/hello1?test' -H 'Cookie: DEVICEID=f301M6ud0R base64_decode(QBxnBCN0MV-RO9VeI9vgcAcBaLq1y'

{"message":"Your request cookie is not allowed"}




